data.description: A cozy front porch will welcome you to this well-kept 3 bedroom 2 bath home in desirable Bonita Vista subdivision. An open floor plan, back covered patio, and large backyard are perfect for entertaining guests. The living room features a cozy wood-burning rock fireplace that adds warmth and charm to the space. Plenty of seating provided by island breakfast bar, dining room, and breakfast area. The primary bedroom features an en suite bathroom with a walk-in shower, double vanity, and spacious closet. Stained concrete floors for easy maintanence. Laundry room has open shelving. Attached double car garage with opener.
